Package: Prepare
Type: Package
Title: Streamlines Data Cleaning for Various Public Datasets that have unique data formatting
Version: 1.2.1
Author: Chasen Jeffries
Maintainer: Chasen Jeffries <chasen.jeffries@cgu.edu>
Description: This package provides functions to streamline the data cleaning process 
    for various public datasets, especially those with unique formatting challenges. 
    It includes specialized functions for handling data from sources like the World Bank 
    and United Nations, offering options for reshaping, cleaning, and preparing data for analysis.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/Chasen-Jeffries/Prepare
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    dplyr,
    tidyr,
    countrycode
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
